original_title: ONE Friday Fights 17: Pompetch vs. Duangsompong
overview: ONE Friday Fights 17: Pompetch vs. Duangsompong was a combat sports event produced by ONE Championship that took place on May 19, 2023, at Lumpinee Boxing Stadium in Bangkok, Thailand. A 133 pounds catchweight muay thai bout between Pompetch P.K.Saenchai and Duangsompong Jitmuangnon served as the event headliner.
title: ONE Friday Fights 17: Pompetch vs. Duangsompong
